<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/_pages/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/_components/navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/_abstract/root.css" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/jade_logo.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.2/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <title>Jadebot.app</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("../components/navbar.ejs") %>
    <div class="titleBox">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-top">
          <img src="/assets/jade_logo.png" alt="jade logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="header-bottom">
          <h1><span>Enchance</span><br />Your Discord Server</h1>
          <p>
            Echance your discord server with jade! Starboards, moderation,
            backups, all the information in the world, personalized api, and
            much more with jadebot.app
          </p>
          <a href="/invite">Add the bot!</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lowerSection">
        <h1 class="lowerSection__title"><%= userCount %> users are taking advantage of Jade's features!</h1>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-star'></i>
                    <h2>Starboard</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Pin your/your communitys favorite things inside of your own server! Just react to the message with a <i class='bx bxs-star star'></i> for it to be sent into your desinated channel!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-bar-chart-square' ></i>
                    <h2>Leveling</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Level up your server! All you too keep track of your server members activity, allowing you to reward them! Add your own custom level role requirements, multipliers and more!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-backpack' ></i>
                    <h2>Moderation</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Make sure your server is safe and secure with Jade! Warn, Ban, Kick, Keep track of previous cases and so much more all comes included with jade moderation!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-hard-hat' ></i>
                    <h2>Management</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Allow jade to take care of your server mangement. Manage your roles, channels and much more through jade's simple yet effective slash commands!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-brain' ></i>
                    <h2>Suggestions</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Allow taking in community feedback to be easier with jade! Allow members to suggest ideas etc, vote on them and finalise your own decision on them.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="title">
                    <i class='bx bxs-virus-block' ></i>
                    <h2>Join Gate</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Setup personal join gates for your server! Force new members to meet certain requirements other wise jade will take action! Easily manage these gates, aswell as changing the action!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
             
        </div>
    
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
